删除重复记录只保留最新一条
delete from goods_detail_draft WHERE (goods_detail_draft.goods_id) 
IN ( SELECT goods_detail_draft.goods_id FROM goods_detail_draft where goods_detail_draft.update_date > to_date('2016-08-29','yyyy-mm-dd')
GROUP BY goods_detail_draft.goods_id HAVING COUNT(goods_detail_draft.goods_id) > 1) 
AND ROWID NOT IN (SELECT Max(ROWID) FROM goods_detail_draft GROUP BY goods_detail_draft.goods_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1);

删除重复记录只保留最旧一条
delete from goods_detail_draft WHERE (goods_detail_draft.goods_id) 
IN ( SELECT goods_detail_draft.goods_id FROM goods_detail_draft GROUP BY goods_detail_draft.goods_id HAVING COUNT(goods_detail_draft.goods_id) > 1) 
AND ROWID NOT IN (SELECT MIN(ROWID) FROM goods_detail_draft GROUP BY goods_detail_draft.goods_id HAVING COUNT(*) > 1);


create or replace procedure deleteGoods(@goodsId in number)as
begin 
delete from Goods_Image_Resources where Goods_Image_Resources.Img_Id = (select Goods_Image.Id  from Goods_Image where Goods_Image.Id = (select GOODS_DETAIL.Img_Res_Id from GOODS_DETAIL where GOODS_DETAIL.GOODS_ID = @goodsId));
delete from Goods_Image where Goods_Image.Id = (select GOODS_DETAIL.Img_Res_Id from GOODS_DETAIL where GOODS_DETAIL.GOODS_ID = @goodsId);
delete from GOODS_DETAIL where GOODS_DETAIL.GOODS_ID = @goodsId;
delete from Goods_Info where Goods_Info.Goods_Id = @goodsId;
end;

DECLARE
  ddt_id NUMBER(38);
  BEGIN
  for ddt_id in (select ddt.goods_id from GOODS_IMAGE_RESOURCES t,Goods_Detail ddt where t.img_width is null and t.img_id = ddt.Img_Res_Id) loop
